---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Voidless Tale">
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Voidless Tale</h1>
    <p>Between Heaven and Hell, your choices echo.</p>
    <div class="button-row">
      <a class="btn" href="/devlog/">Devlog</a>
      <a class="btn" href="/smith/">Voidless Smith</a>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="card"><h2>Heaven vs Hell</h2><p>Walk a fractured path where devotion and rebellion both demand a cost.</p></section>
  <section class="card"><h2>Seven Deadly Sins</h2><p>Each sin changes combat, dialogue, and the world that answers your presence.</p></section>
  <section class="card"><h2>Loot, crafting, skill absorption</h2><p>Harvest relics, forge upgrades, and absorb defeated skills to alter your build.</p></section>
  <section class="card"><h2>Voidless Smith tooling</h2><p>Our internal tooling is evolving into a creator-focused pixel weapon generator.</p></section>
</BaseLayout>
